{Speech 2}{}{The Master will forgive your sins! Join us and be free! Praise to the Master and his mercy!@@Hello, friend! The Master's vision has made me truly alive for the first time. May I share my wonderful story with you?@@You are in charge, friend, but the Master is your guide. Praise the Master! Praise the Holy Flame that lights our way!@@The Master looks above! The Master sits below! Watch the Peace and the Unity grow!@@Praise the Master! Praise the Holy Flame! Praise the Vineyard of Life! Whee!@@No story ends in death, as long as the Master is here to protect us!}
